author: Home Repair Tutor
description:
This video shares how to transition from one tile floor to another in a doorway. I'm using Schluter's RENO-TK aluminum profile.

#tilefloor #bathroomremodel #diy #homerepairtutor   

Tile Floor Doorway Transition Tips
0:00 Tile floor doorway transition
0:06 How to cut Schluter metal profile
0:27 How to install Schluter metal profile in doorway

These supplies were used in our video:

-Schluter RENO-TK
-Milwaukee Metal Cutting Circular Saw 2782-20
-Perfect Level Master T-Lock System for tile
